ch.obermuhlner.jhuge.collection.builder

Interface SetBuilder<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of the element in the Set
    All Superinterfaces:
    CollectionBuilder<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractHugeSetBuilder, HugeHashSet.Builder, ImmutableHugeHashSet.Builder, ImmutableHugeHashSet2.Builder

    public interface SetBuilder<E>
extends CollectionBuilder<E>
    Builds a Set.

    The concrete implementations of this API are typically inner classes of the collection class they are building.
